::DrillBit::

DrillBit back away from KitKat, letting her sleep. He heard StarScreams
babble. And then faced the other bots.
"Blugeon, Terrorsaur, go check out the ruins of the old base. Please."
He turned to Atma.
"Ok, mr. Former General, you think we should head for the cave?"
